From Bruce Gendler Subject X GL widget translation problem I am writing a custom widget to support the display of graphics and The user of the widget will be able to specify when creating it whether it is to operate in X or GL I have set up translations and actions to handle mouse button They work fine when the widget is in X In GL mode they only work when the widget my GL X widget is a child of a Put another way the translations do not work when the widget is configured in GL mode and is a child of a Does anyone know why this is happening Thanks in Bruce Gendler